name: MXAppLaunchMetric
desc: An object representing metrics about app launch time.

items.name: var histogrammedOptimizedTimeToFirstDraw: MXHistogram<UnitDuration>
items.desc: A histogram of the different amounts of time associated with prewarmed app launches.

items.name: var histogrammedTimeToFirstDraw: MXHistogram<UnitDuration>
items.desc: A histogram of the different amounts of time taken to launch the app.

items.name: var histogrammedApplicationResumeTime: MXHistogram<UnitDuration>
items.desc: A histogram of the different amounts of time taken to resume the app from the background.
